title: Ravens’ Harbaugh say he’s not after payback
text:
Photo: Matt Slocum, Associated Press Ravens coach John Harbaugh (left, with then-49ers coach Jim Harbaugh in 2013) has suddenly become a Michigan fan — although he likes Ohio State alum Carlos Hyde, of the 49ers. Ravens coach John Harbaugh (left, with then-49ers coach Jim...
Early in his conference call with the Bay Area media Wednesday, Baltimore head coach John Harbaugh complimented Carlos Hyde while noting the 49ers’ running back attended a school that counts Michigan as it its rival.
